These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, kale, pepper, radish
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, helicopter, boat, trike
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, electrician, scientist, chef
 1. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating radish is on the right of the analyst##1
 3. the scientist is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
 4. the analyst is not the person eating radish##6
 5. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
 6. the electrician is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 7. the scientist is not to the left of the person eating kale##8
 8. the person eating kale is not the chef##6
 9. the person eating apple is not the person driving the trike##6
10. the electrician is the person driving the trike##1
11. the person eating kale is not to the right of the scientist##8
12. the person eating kale is in an even position##4
13. the person eating radish is not to the right of the chef##8
14. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the scientist##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | apple         | radish     | pepper     | kale         |
| Transport   | helicopter | trike    | boat     | taxi |
| Job   | analyst       | electrician | chef | scientist       |

