.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, orchid, lily, sunflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, librarian, pilot
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, white, ivory, blue
 1. the librarian is not to the right of the pilot##8
 2. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is the freelancer##1
 5. the electrician is not the person who growslily##6
 6. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Flower   | lily          | dahlia      | sunflower      | orchid   |
| Job        | librarian     | electrician | freelancer | pilot      |
| Color      | blue | white    | green  | ivory |

