.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, potato, peach, peas
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, d&b, techno
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, bellflower, marigold, balloon-flower
 1. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 2. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
 3. the person eating papaya is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 4. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
 5. the person who growsorchid is not the fan of blues##6
 6. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 7. the fan of blues is not to the right of the fan of techno##8
 8. the person eating peas is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 9. the person eating potato is in an even position##4
10. the person eating peas is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food         | peach  | potato | peas | papaya |
| Music-Genre   | country  | blues      | techno | d&b        |
| Flower     | orchid | marigold       | balloon-flower    | bellflower     |

