.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, horror, mystery, thriller
4 different games are played: monopoly, poker, backgammon, billiard
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, train, jet-ski
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 2. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
 3. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
 6. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 7. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the train##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is the person driving the train##1
11. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | thriller | horror    | mystery |
| Game   | backgammon    | poker     | monopoly   | billiard     |
| Transport   | helicopter | train   | subway | jet-ski    |

