.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, hiking, reading
There 4 different types of food: orange, pepper, strawberry, cabbage
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, light-blue, purple, mauve
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person who likes light-blue##5
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 3. the person eating orange is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 6. the person eating cabbage is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the person who likes purple##6
 8. the person eating pepper is the person who likes purple##1
 9. the person eating strawberry is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
10. the person who likes mauve is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who likes mauve is not to the left of the person eating strawberry##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | hiking       | card-games | gardening  | reading    |
| Food   | strawberry       | cabbage    | pepper | orange    |
| Color         | mauve | coral   | purple   | light-blue |

