.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, grapes, plum, potato
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, september, february, november
4 different pets are kept: frog, fish, chinchilla, lizard
 1. the person eating plum is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is not the owner of the fish##6
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the person eating grapes and the person who's birthday is in november##7
 4. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 8. the owner of the lizard is between the person eating blueberry and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the right of the person eating blueberry##8
10. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person eating potato##8
11. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | grapes      | plum      | potato | blueberry |
| Birthday   | february | january    | november | september     |
| Pet   | frog    | chinchilla | lizard  | fish |

