 1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the malaysian##1
 2. the chinese is not the person who likes lilac##6
 3. the chinese is between the malaysian and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 4. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is not the polish##6
 8. the person who likes aquamarine is not to the right of the polish##8
 9. the polish is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
10. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
11. the person who likes aquamarine is not to the left of the polish##8
12. the person who likes lilac is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
13. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Color   | pink   | purple | lilac        | aquamarine |
| Nationality   | malaysian | chinese   | indonesian | polish     |
| Birthday     | june      | july      | may      | november        |

