City: hannover, edinburgh, boston, marseilles
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
1. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##5
2. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to boston##7
3. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
4. the fan of pop is not to the right of the victorian house##8
5. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5
6. the person traveling to hannover is not to the right of the futuristic house##8
7. the person traveling to marseilles is the fan of jazz##1
8. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere between the fan of rock and the ranch-style house##7
9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| House      | ranch-style     | colonial | futuristic  | victorian |
| City          | edinburgh | marseilles   | hannover | boston |
| Music-Genre   | house     | jazz   | rock      | pop      |

