.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, magic-tricks, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, rowing, swimming, badminton
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, bolivar, oliveros, baccarat
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere between the baccarat-smoker and the person who's sport is swimming##7
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the bolivar-smoker##8
 4. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 8. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the old-henry-smoker##8
10. the oliveros-smoker is not to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
11. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
13. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
14. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | drawing    | magic-tricks | woodworking | fishing    |
| Sport   | swimming  | badminton    | handball      | rowing |
| Cigar     | bolivar | old-henry          | baccarat      | oliveros       |

