.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, juice, milk
House: art-deco, tower, modern, wooden
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, airplane, subway, skateboard
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
 2. the modern house is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
 3. the wooden house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the modern house is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 5. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 6. the person driving the subway is the modern house##1
 7. the tower house is not to the right of the modern house##8
 8. the modern house is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
 9. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
10. the modern house is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
11. the art-deco house is not the person drinking iced-tea##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice     | milk  | iced-tea | almond-milk |
| House           | tower | modern | wooden | art-deco   |
| Transport   | skateboard | subway  | airplane   | bus   |

